GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
H 1
HOUSE BILL 1036
Short Title: Funds for Caswell County Vol. Fire Department. (Public)
Sponsors: Representative Price.
For a complete list of sponsors, refer to the North Carolina General Assembly web site.
Referred to: Appropriations, if favorable, Rules, Calendar, and Operations of the House
April 23, 2026
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE FUNDS TO CASWELL COUNTY FOR THE REPLACEMENT
3 OF THE CASVILLE VOLUNTEER FIRE DEPARTMENT'S FACILITY.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Office of State
6 Budget and Management the sum of one million seven hundred thousand dollars ($1,700,000) in
7 nonrecurring funds for the 2026-2027 fiscal year to provide a directed grant to Caswell County
8 for the replacement of the Casville Volunteer Fire Department's facility.
9 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2026.
*H1036-v-1*

